<section xmlns="http://xml.house.gov/schemas/uslm/1.0" style="-uslm-lc:I80" id="id7851bc3b-6992-11f1-ab3f-8b4c043f8cd5" identifier="/us/usc/t16/s583j–6"><num value="583j–6">§ 583j–6.</num><heading> United States release from liability</heading><content>
<p style="-uslm-lc:I11" class="indent0">The United States shall not be liable for any debts, defaults, acts or omissions of the Foundation nor shall the full faith and credit of the United States extend to any obligations of the Foundation.</p>
</content><sourceCredit id="id7851bc3c-6992-11f1-ab3f-8b4c043f8cd5">(<ref href="/us/pl/101/593/tIV/s408">Pub. L. 101–593, title IV, § 408</ref>, <date date="1990-11-16">Nov. 16, 1990</date>, <ref href="/us/stat/104/2973">104 Stat. 2973</ref>.)</sourceCredit>
</section>
